<table border="0" height="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="1007" style="background:url(images/bg1.jpg)" align="center">
<!-- fwtable fwsrc="未命名" fwbase="sr.jpg" fwstyle="Dreamweaver" fwdocid = "1344182167" fwnested="1" -->
  <tr><!-- row 1 -->
    <td align="right" valign="top">
    
		<!--标题开始-->
	      <div style="font-family:'华文行楷'; font-size:18pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center; padding-top:15px;">
	      	道教辞典
	      </div>
	      <!-- 副标题 -->
	      <div style="font-family:'华文行楷'; font-size:16pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center; padding-top:15px;">
	      	
	      </div>
	      <!--标题结束-->
		<div style="text-align:center"><a name="1" id="1"></a>
		<img name="sr_r3_c1" src="images/sr_r3_c1.gif" width="293" height="32" border="0" id="sr_r3_c1" alt="" /></div>
		<!--图片-->
		
		<!--图片结束-->
		<!-- 作者 -->
		
			<div style="font-family:'宋体'; font-size:12pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center;padding-bottom:8px;">
		      	
		    </div>
		
	   <div style="text-align:left; color:#88510c; font-size:14px; line-height:20px; width:900px; height:auto; margin:0 auto;">
	   		<!-- 显示内容 -->
	   		<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">神&nbsp;<font face="Times New Roman">(1)</font><font face="宋体">指鬼神或天神。有神论者认为，鬼神或天神是流行于天地之间具有人格的精气和元气，或人死后而独立存在的精神意识。《管子&middot;内业》</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;凡物之精，此</font><font face="Times New Roman">(</font><font face="宋体">比</font><font face="Times New Roman">)</font><font face="宋体">则为生</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">下生五谷，上为列星</font><font face="Times New Roman">;</font><font face="宋体">流行天地之间，谓之鬼神</font><font face="Times New Roman">;</font><font face="宋体">&hellip;&hellip;是故民</font><font face="Times New Roman">(</font><font face="宋体">名</font><font face="Times New Roman">)</font><font face="宋体">气。&rdquo;意谓鬼神也是一种精气。《周氏冥通记》</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;夫生为人，实依依世上</font><font face="Times New Roman">;</font><font face="宋体">死为神，则恋恋于幽冥。&rdquo;《混元皇帝圣纪》</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;老君者，乃元气。&rdquo;老君，是道教所信奉的最高天神。作为天神之&ldquo;神&rdquo;，如老君等，为道教气功的意想对象，名之曰&ldquo;存思&rdquo;或&ldquo;存神&rdquo;。</font><font face="Times New Roman">(2)</font><font face="宋体">指&ldquo;道&rdquo;或&ldquo;一&rdquo;。邵雍《观外物篇》</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;道与一，神之强名也。&rdquo;</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">(3)<font face="宋体">指天。《榖梁传&middot;昭公十八年》</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;天者，神。&rdquo;《书经&middot;大诰》</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;天命不易。&rdquo;认为天就是有意志的神或上帝，是万事万物的主宰者。在佛教、道教中所说的&ldquo;诸天&rdquo;，往往就指诸神。</font><font face="Times New Roman">(4)</font><font face="宋体">指奥妙的变化或造化。《易&middot;系辞上》</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;阴阳不测之谓神。&rdquo;《荀子&middot;天论》</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;不见其事而见其功，夫是之谓神。&rdquo;</font><font face="Times New Roman">(5)</font><font face="宋体">指人的精神。《史记&middot;太史公自序》</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;神大用则竭。&rdquo;《遵生八笺》卷一引寒山子曰</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;修生之道，除嗜去欲，啬神保和。&rdquo;在气功学上，有神论者认为，人经过气功修炼，精神可以出游。《太平广记》卷七十八《符契元传》</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;能于入静日，多神游诸岳。&rdquo;《周氏冥通记》</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;从乙未八月以后，游行诸处，此皆是神去而身实不动也。&rdquo;</font><font face="Times New Roman">(6)</font><font face="宋体">指身神。道教认为，人体有三万六千身神，经过气功修炼，身神可以举形飞升。</font><font face="Times New Roman">(7)</font><font face="宋体">指与&ldquo;魄&rdquo;相对的&ldquo;魂&rdquo;。《遵生八笺》卷一引《黄帝中经》曰</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;神者，魂也，降之于天</font><font face="Times New Roman">;</font><font face="宋体">鬼者，魄也，经之于地。&rdquo;</font><font face="Times New Roman">(8)</font><font face="宋体">指人的生理功能和知觉。《证治准绳》</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;神之在人大矣，在足能行，在手能握，在舌能言，在鼻能嗅，在耳能听，在目能视。&rdquo;</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">(9)<font face="宋体">指本性及其妙用。《悟真篇注疏》七绝之四十二注</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;性即神也。&rdquo;《金仙证论》</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">静者性，妙用为神也。&rdquo;这里所说的&ldquo;性&rdquo;，均指本性。</font><font face="Times New Roman">(10)</font><font face="宋体">指&ldquo;良知&rdquo;的妙用。王阳明《传习录》</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;良知，&hellip;&hellip;以其妙用而言谓之神也。&rdquo;</font><font face="Times New Roman">(11)</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;内丹&rdquo;的，&ldquo;三宝&rdquo;或&ldquo;三药&rdquo;之一。内丹家谓天、地、人三才各有&ldquo;三宝&rdquo;，人之&ldquo;三宝&rdquo;则为精、气、神，又称此&ldquo;三宝&rdquo;为&ldquo;三药&rdquo;，或&ldquo;上药三品&rdquo;。宋翁葆光在《紫阳真人悟真直指详说三乘秘要》举出神的异名、代号和隐语有</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">离、卯、甲、东、三、八、木、日魂、乌髓、姹女、青娥、真汞、木液、火汞、火龙、金乌、雌母、流珠、红铅、朱砂、交梨、玉芝、真火、水银、日中乌、龙弦气、赤凤髓、砂里汞、离之己、山头月白、青衣女子、碧眼胡儿、乌肝八两、生于丙丁、二八姹女、朱砂鼎内、下弦半斤，凡</font><font face="Times New Roman">37</font><font face="宋体">种。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: right; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">(<font face="宋体">杨福程</font><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">灵宝&nbsp;<font face="Times New Roman">(1)</font><font face="宋体">道教派别之一，传《洞玄灵宝经》。《道藏源流考》</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;今之《灵宝经》，东晋末叶葛巢甫</font><font face="Times New Roman">(</font><font face="宋体">葛洪之孙</font><font face="Times New Roman">)</font><font face="宋体">所造。至宋文、明二帝时，陆修静更增修，立成仪轨，于是灵宝之教大行于世。&rdquo;</font><font face="Times New Roman">(2)</font><font face="宋体">道教&ldquo;三清&rdquo;尊神之一&mdash;&mdash;&ldquo;上清灵宝天尊&rdquo;的简称。据说由&ldquo;灵宝丈人&rdquo;</font><font face="Times New Roman">(</font><font face="宋体">赤混太无之气</font><font face="Times New Roman">)</font><font face="宋体">化生，与天宝君、神宝君并为三洞教主。《灵宝洞玄自然九天生神章经》</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;天宝诵之，以开天地之光，灵宝诵之，以开九幽长夜之魂</font><font face="Times New Roman">;</font><font face="宋体">神宝诵之，以制万灵。&rdquo;</font><font face="Times New Roman">(3)</font><font face="宋体">指天地间神灵和珍宝。《洞玄灵宝定观经》</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;灵者，神也，在天曰灵，宝者，珍也，在地曰宝。天有灵化，神用不测，则广覆无边，地有众宝，济养群品，则厚载万物。&rdquo;</font><font face="Times New Roman">(4)</font><font face="宋体">指神与精。《元气论》</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;行</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">此道者<font face="Times New Roman">(</font><font face="宋体">按</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">指练气功之人</font><font face="Times New Roman">)</font><font face="宋体">，谓常思灵宝。灵者，神也</font><font face="Times New Roman">;</font><font face="宋体">宝者，精也。&rdquo;</font><font face="Times New Roman">(5)</font><font face="宋体">指神与气。《脉望》</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;灵者，神也，宝者，气也。形者，灵宝之宅舍也。&rdquo;按</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">今之气功所称&ldquo;灵宝&rdquo;者，皆源于道教。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: right; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">(<font face="宋体">杨福程</font><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<!--EndFragment-->
	   </div>
	   <div style="text-align:left; color:#88510c; font-size:14px; line-height:20px; width:900px; height:auto; margin:0 auto;">
	   		<!-- 附件 -->
	   		
		   		
			
	   </div>
   
   
